<p>based on: <a href="https://askubuntu.com/questions/871825/add-more-disk-space-for-linux-from-windows-in-a-dual-bootable-machine">link 1</a>, <a href="https://askubuntu.com/questions/727112/give-more-hard-disk-space-to-ubuntu?rq=1">link 2</a>. link 2 has many links to solve
