<ol>
  <li>
    <p>go to windows â€œDisk Managementâ€ and then look at the large
partition that you wanna split and then unallocate it.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Make a live USB of Ubuntu so that you can manipulate Ubuntu. Follow
<a href="https://ubuntu.com/tutorials/create-a-usb-stick-on-ubuntu#1-overview">these instructions</a> word-for-word and that is good enough.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
